title: C F Financial completes acquisition of Peoples Bankshares
content:
C F Financial  CFFI  0 8   announced that it has completed the acquisition of Peoples Bankshares  Incorporated  OTCPK PBVA   effective January 1  2020  Peoples shareholders are entitled to receive 0 5366 shares of C F Financial s common stock and  27 00 in cash for each share of Peoples common stock 
With the addition of Peoples  C F Financial would have had   1 8B in assets   1 2B in total gross loans outstanding and  1 5B in total deposits on a combined basis at December 31  2019
